PERSONAL MEDIA SERVER




DEPLOYING SERVER:

After downloading, edit nginx.conf
Change "domainname" to your host's domain

You must also edit the docker-compose.yaml to fit your configuration.
Change "domainname" to your host's domain
Change path bindings to desired storage locations for storage.

After completing previous steps, server is ready for deployment.

Run the following command:

	 docker compose up -d

After changes, you may add the following flags

--force-recreate: forces a new container to be created regardless of existing
--remove-orphans: prunes containers removed from compose

